-- Housebuilder Barratt appoints John Allan as chairman designate
-- 
-- Tue Mar 11, 2014 03:20AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, March 11 (Reuters) - Barratt Developments <BDEV.L> has appointed Dixons Retail's <DXNS.L> current chairman, John Allan, as its chairman designate, the British housebuilder said on Tuesday.

Allan will replace Bob Lawson who has chaired Britain's largest housebuilder by volume since July 2008. He will join the board on Aug. 1 and will succeed Lawson on Nov. 12.